item.description:
tibco-twilio This activity provides your flogo application the ability to send a SMS via Twilio.
Installation flogo add activity github.com/TIBCOSoftware/flogo-contrib/activity/twilio  Schema Inputs and Outputs:
{ &quot;input&quot;:[ { &quot;name&quot;: &quot;accountSID&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot; }, { &quot;name&quot;: &quot;authToken&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot; }, { &quot;name&quot;: &quot;from&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot; }, { &quot;name&quot;: &quot;to&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot; }, { &quot;name&quot;: &quot;message&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot; } ], &quot;output&quot;: [] }  Settings    Setting Description     accountSID The Twilio account SID   authToken The Twilio auth token   from The Twilio number you are sending the SMS from   to The number you are sending the SMS to   message The SMS message    Note: Phone numbers should be in the format &lsquo;+15555555555&rsquo;
